 <summary>PHP_CodeSniffer sniff pool of the TYPO3 Project</summary>
 <description>This package contains custom sniffs which are compatible with the PHP_CodeSniffer.
Understand this package as a sniff pool which contains all needed custom sniffs for the TYPO3CMS and TYPO3Flow Coding Guidelines.
Additionally you must install the specific pear package for your preferred Coding Guidelines.</description>
